org.apache.poi.hslf.record

Class ExHyperlinkAtom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.RecordAtom
        • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.ExHyperlinkAtom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord 

    public final class ExHyperlinkAtom
extends RecordAtom
    Tne atom that holds metadata on a specific Link in the document. (The actual link is held in a sibling CString record)(保存文档中特定链接上的元数据的原子。(The实际链接保存在兄弟C字符串记录中）)
    Author:
    Nick Burch
